    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXIV. Nodalla.\nDahwids ſkaita tohs Laudis : 1. To Israëlites\nru Pulks bija aſtonſmits reisi tuhſloſchi\nſipri Wihti : 9. Dahwids atſhſt/ ka wiſch\ntapehz lohti grehkojs : 10. Kad wiṅnam\ntohp uſlikts no trim Mohzibahm weenu iſ\nwehleht / iſwehle wiṅch Mehri : 11 / 14.\nRo furras mirre ſeptindeſmits tuhſloſchi\nWihti eekſch trim Deenahm : 15. Dahwidē\nDeewu lubdspor teem Laudim : 17. Uppure-\nun ſalihdſina Deewu/ kas to Mohzibu no\nwehrſch: 25."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tas KUNGS eeduf\nmojabs wehl lohti pah\nIsraëlu : (Jo Satans\nLait: Gr: 22/ 1.) ſkubbinaj\nDahwidu pretti teem/ un fazzi-\nja : Eij/ ſkaiti Israëlu un Juhdú"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Rehnixſch fazzija\nus Joabu to Karra Leel-Kun-\ngu/ kas pee wiña bija: Eij jel-\nle apfahrt zaur wiſſahm Israë-\nZiltim/ no Dannas lihds Verſe-\nbai/ un ſkaſtajt tohs Laudis/ k-\nes to Lauschu Pulku finnu. Ta-\nfazzija Joabs us to Rehnixu:"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lai tas KUNGS tai-\nDeeivs pee ſcheim Laudim ſim-\nkahrt wairak peeleek/ ka mann-\nKunga ta Rehnixa Azzisto red-\nkapehz tad mannain Kunga-\ntam Rehnixaim ſchi Leeta gri-\nbahs?"
    }
